        <li>Weather-sealed camera body</li>
        <li>16-35mm wide-angle lens</li>
        <li>Sturdy tripod</li>
        <li>Remote shutter release</li>
        <li>Microfiber cloths for rain</li>
      </ul>

      <blockquote>
